Package resources

Contains all the classes for reading external files and interpreting them.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KeyBoardListener
    Listens for keyboard inputs and may process multiple inputs simultaneously.
    LevelLoader
    Loads the level from system memory.
    SpriteSheetReader
    The SpriteSheetReader class is intended for extracting sprite sheets from image files, SpriteSheetReader has one public method which fetches the sprite sheet from a target path.
    TextFileReader
    Contains the basic file IO processes used by the resource managers.

Package resources Description
